ven%20repayment%20plans%2C%20which%20won't%20be%20implemented%20until%20July%201%2C%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20will%20soon%20start%20seeing%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20they%20borrow%20and%20pay%20off%20their%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20into%20law%20his%20tax%20and%20spending%20bill%2C%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20changes%20to%20student-loan%20repayment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20announced%20it%20was%20beginning%20to%20implement%20some%20of%20the%20new%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20wrote%20in%20a%20July%2018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsapartners.ed.gov%2Fknowledge-center%2Flibrary%2Fdear-colleague-letters%2F2025-07-18%2Ffederal-student-loan-program-provisions-effective-upon-enactment-under-one-big-beautiful-bill-act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20spending%20law%20will%20be%20implemented%20on%20July%201%2C%202026%2C%20including%20the%20creation%20of%20two%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans.%20However%2C%20the%20department%20said%20it%20is%20working%20with%20student-loan%20servicers%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20series%20of%20changes%20before%20then%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENo%20longer%20requiring%20borrowers%20to%20have%20partial%20financial%20hardship%20to%20qualify%20for%20an%20income-based%20repayment%20plan%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExpanding%20options%20for%20borrowers%20who%20took%20out%20parent%20PLUS%20loans%20to%20enroll%20in%20an%20income-based%20repayment%20plan%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReducing%20the%20amount%20a%20student%20can%20borrow%20if%20they're%20enrolled%20in%20a%20program%20that%20is%20not%20full-time%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnd%20delaying%20the%20implementation%20of%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20borrower%20defense%20to%20repayment%20and%20closed%20school%20discharge%20regulations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20borrower%20believes%20they%20were%20defrauded%20by%20the%20school%20they%20attended%2C%20they%20can%20apply%20for%20borrower%20defense%2C%20and%20if%20their%20claims%20are%20approved%2C%20their%20loans%20will%20be%20forgiven.%20Biden's%20administration%20attempted%20to%20make%20the%20process%20easier%20for%20borrowers%20to%20navigate%2C%20but%20it%20was%20blocked%20in%20court%20and%20never%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActing%20Undersecretary%20James%20Bergeron%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20statement%20that%20Trump's%20spending%20bill%20%26quot%3Bdelivers%20for%20student%20borrowers%20in%20a%20big%20way%20%E2%80%94%20simplifying%20the%20student%20loan%20repayment%20system%2C%20funding%20the%20%2410.5%20billion%20shortfall%20in%20Pell%20Grant%20funding%20left%20by%20the%20previous%20administration%2C%20supporting%20short-term%20career%20focused%20programs%20that%20train%20workers%20for%20in-demand%20jobs%2C%20and%20holding%20colleges%20accountable%20by%20eliminating%20student%20loan%20eligibility%20for%20programs%20that%20leave%20students%20worse%20off%20than%20if%20they%20had%20never%20enrolled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20announcement%20is%20the%20first%20step%20in%20the%20implementation%20process%2C%20and%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20building%20the%20President's%20vision%20for%20education%20and%20training%20beyond%20high%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20Bergeron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department's%20letter%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20amending%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-changes-pslf-student-loan-forgiveness-employer-eligibility-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments%2C%20to%20allow%20payments%20made%20under%20a%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20to%20count%20toward%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20spending%20bill%20eliminates%20existing%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20and%20replaces%20them%20with%20two%20options%3A%20a%20standard%20repayment%20plan%20and%20a%20new%20Repayment%20Assistance%20Plan%2C%20which%20sets%20borrowers'%20monthly%20payments%20at%201%25%20to%2010%25%20of%20their%20income%2C%20with%20any%20remaining%20balance%20forgiven%20after%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20options%20are%20less%20generous%20than%20the%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20which%20the%20bill%20eliminates.%20SAVE%20would%20have%20allowed%20for%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20with%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20debt%20relief.%20The%20department%20announced%20on%20July%209%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-student-loan-borrowers-when-does-interest-restart-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterest%20charges%20will%20restart%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20balances%20of%20the%208%20million%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20more%20information%20on%20changes%20to%20repayment%20from%20the%20spending%20bill%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20and%20months.%20They%20come%20as%20the%20administration%20is%20working%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-dismantling-department-education-means-supreme-court-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edismantle%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20on%20July%2014%20that%20Trump%20can%20proceed%20with%20firing%20department%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeautiful-bill-trump-starts-implementing-student-loan-debt-repayment-changes-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%2