%2Fi.insider.com%2F68792cfbf748d8c055f5cfb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EResearch%20from%20Honeywell%20found%20that%2080%25%20of%20retailers%20will%20acquire%20AI%20systems%20over%20the%20coming%20months.%3Cp%3EBus%C3%A0%20Photography%2F%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELowe's%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20optimize%20store%20layouts%20and%20meet%20changing%20customer%20needs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EComputer%20vision%20models%20can%20also%20offer%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20for%20retailers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-everything%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20Is%20Changing%20Everything%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20on%20AI%20adoption%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20time%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcmo-jennifer-wilson-lowes-influencer-marketing-leadership-cannes-lions-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estop%20by%20Lowe's%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20new%20house%20plant%2C%20supplies%20to%20prepare%20for%20hurricane%20season%2C%20or%20a%20part%20to%20fix%20a%20bathroom%20leak%2C%20the%20quantity%20and%20in-store%20location%20of%20the%20product%20will%20likely%20have%20been%20influenced%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-target-use-ai-to-prevent-inventory-shortages-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home-improvement%20retailer%20is%20using%20AI%20systems%20to%20develop%20a%20greater%20understanding%20of%20fast-changing%20customer%20needs%20and%20expectations%20and%20to%20optimize%20its%20store%20layouts%20accordingly.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20plant%2C%20AI%20could%20predict%20growing%20demand%20for%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20seasonal%20shrub%20and%20increase%20its%20orders%20as%20interest%20rises%2C%20then%20place%20the%20plants%20in%20the%20most%20obvious%20in-store%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20hurricane%20preparedness%2C%20sudden%20weather%20changes%20can%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20to%20order%20larger%20volumes%20of%20flashlights%20and%20weather%20radios.%20And%20plumbing%20items%20may%20be%20placed%20closer%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20store%20for%20leaks%20that%20require%20emergency%20attention%20during%20harsh%20and%20unpredictable%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChandhu%20Nair%2C%20the%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20data%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20innovation%20at%20Lowe's%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20technology%20is%20allowing%20the%20store%20chain%20to%20create%20more%20immersive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-revolutionizing-customer-experience-ai-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshopping%20experiences%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20also%20easy%20and%20quick%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20effort%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20front-of-house%20retail%20staff%20and%20white-collar%20workers%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20who%20are%20ensuring%20that%20AI%20augments%20rather%20than%20replaces%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9f1fd96-2997-436f-b908-69e66c52ccaf%5C%22%3EA%20team-wide%20effort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENair%20said%20that%20delivering%20a%20%26quot%3Bsimpler%2C%20faster%2C%20and%20more%20fun%26quot%3B%20physical%20retail%20experience%20requires%20large%20volumes%20of%20real-world%20data%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Bstore%20traffic%20patterns%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blocal%20preferences%2C%26quot%3B%20provided%20by%20store%20associates%20and%20customers.%20It%20also%20needs%20the%20right%20tools%20for%20Lowe's%20spatial%20planning%20teams%20to%20extract%20meaningful%20insights%20from%20it%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20these%20teams%20relied%20largely%20on%20manual%20processes%20for%20collecting%20this%20information%2C%20analyzing%20it%2C%20and%20putting%20the%20insights%20into%20practice.%20Consequently%2C%20Nair%20said%20it%20could%20take%20months%20for%20Lowe's%20to%20see%20any%20meaningful%20results.%20But%20AI-powered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-model-ai-explained-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espatial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20have%20reduced%20this%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20fraction%20of%20that%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENair%20said%20this%20is%20paramount%20because%20new%20product%20trends%20are%20always%20emerging%20and%20disappearing%2C%20especially%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-trends-for-marketers-niche-influencers-ai-report-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20apps%20like%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20now%20swap%20layouts%20more%20frequently%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20reflecting%20what%20customers%20in%20that%20area%20need%20at%20that%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20spatial%20intelligence%20and%20data%20analysis%20tools%2C%20Lowe's%20is%20also%20exploring%20the%20potential%20of%20digital%20twins%20%E2%80%94%20a%20piece%20of%20software%20that%20generates%20a%20virtual%20version%20of%20a%20physical%20environment%2C%20such%20as%20a%20retail%20store.%20Nair%20said%20the%20company%20has%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%203D%20graphics%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Omniverse%2C%20to%20create%20an%20early-stage%20app%20that%20offers%20sales%20and%20inventory%20data%2C%20automatically%20sorts%20stock%2C%20generates%203D%20versions%20of%20its%20physical%20assets%2C%20and%20more%20from%20a%20single%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20ultimately%20gets%20adopted%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20give%20merchants%20a%20way%20to%20test%20and%20refine%20layouts%20digitally%20before%20making%20changes%20in-store%2C%20helping%20surface%20the%20most%20relevant%20products%20in%20ways%20that%20align%20with%20how%20local%20customers%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22faf77e2f-ac1f-4255-ab5f-8f20087c59a7%5C%22%3EAI%20for%20smarter%20shopping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20isn't%20the%20only%20retailer%20that%20believes%20in%20the%20potential%20of%20AI.%20Research%20from%20Honeywell%2C%20a%20multinational%20conglomerate%2C%20found%20that%2080%25%20of%20retailers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.honeywell.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fpress%2F2025%2F01%2Fhoneywell-research-reveals-more-than-80-of-retailers-plan-to-increase-ai-capabilities-in-their-operations-in-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20acquire%20AI%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20coming%20months%20to%20better%20understand%20customers%2C%20create%20a%20more%20efficient%20shopping%20experience%2C%20and%20improve%20worker%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComputer%20vision%20models%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20can%20also%20offer%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20for%20retailers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fvinod-goje%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVinod%20Goje%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20software%20engineering%20leader%20and%20AI%20solutions%20strategist%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20such%20systems%20are%20capable%20of%20generating%20heat%20maps%20that%20signal%20parts%20of%20the%20store%20with%20the%20most%20and%20least%20foot%20traffic%2C%20allowing%20workers%20to%20place%20products%20and%20design%20retail%20layouts%20more%20strategically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoje%20added%20that%20retailers%20can%20also%20install%20computer%20vision%20systems%20on%20shelves%20to%20ensure%20products%20are%20in%20the%20right%20place%20and%20replenished%20when%20stock%20runs%20low.%20The%20tech%20can%20also%20work%20with%20AI%20to%20show%20customers%20personalized%20offers%20on%20in-store%20smart%20screens%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20future%2C%20agentic%20AI%20systems%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20to%20make%20decisions%20independent%20of%20humans%2C%20could%20disrupt%20the%20retail%20sector%20even%20further.%20Sucharita%20Kodali%2C%20principal%20analyst%20at%20market%20research%20firm%20Forrester%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20AI%20agents%20could%20find%20people%20to%20fill%20in%20for%20ill%20employees%2C%20order%20merchandise%20when%20stock%20levels%20are%20low%2C%20and%20develop%20marketing%20plans%20in%20line%20with%20available%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223815bf68-c7d5-49d3-8926-89a07e04e37b%5C%22%3EChallenges%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20as%20retailers%20like%20Lowe's%20become%20more%20reliant%20on%20AI%20to%20improve%20efficiencies%2C%20concerns%20are%20growing%20that%20the%20technology%20could%20wipe%20out%20millions%20of%20blue-collar%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%20That%20said%2C%20Nair%20emphasized%20that%20Lowe's%20approach%20is%20to%20augment%20staff%20and%20not%20put%20them%20out%20of%20work%3B%20using%20AI%20for%20store-layout%20optimization%20requires%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20creativity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20%26quot%3Bdata-powered%20insights%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Befficient%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20concerns%20about%20AI%20adoption%2C%20Nair%20emphasized%20that%20the%20company%20isn't%20using%20%26quot%3Btechnology%20for%20technology's%20sake%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20rather%20focusing%20on%20solutions%20that%20address%20staff's%20biggest%20pain%20points%2C%20based%20on%20feedback%20from%20in-store%20and%20e-commerce%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22653292ac-fa31-4db1-a131-f70a73ac3a40%5C%22%3ELooking%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20of%20Lowe's%20AI%20projects%20are%20still%20in%20their%20infancy%2C%20Nair%20is%20optimistic%20about%20their%20role%20in%20the%20century-old%20retailer's%20future.%20He%20said%20his%20team%20will%20continue%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20better%20at%20connecting%20insights%20and%20predictions%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Badapt%20stores%20even%20faster%26quot%3B%20and%20create%20%26quot%3Bsmarter%20and%20more%20personal%26quot%3B%20experiences%20for%20its%20loyal%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20Nair%20and%20his%20team%20will%20continue%20to%20experiment%20with%20new%20AI%20tools%2C%20improve%20them%20through%20%26quot%3Bquicker%20feedback%20loops%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20strive%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Ba%20high-value%20retail%20experience%20that%20keeps%20evolving%20with%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20excited%20about%20what's%20ahead%20and%20how%20AI%20will%20help%20us%20keep%20solving%20problems%20and%20fulfilling%20dreams%20for%20the%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flowes-ai-retail-store-layout-product-trends-customer-experience-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752866162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68792cfbf748d8c055f5cfb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flowes-ai-retail-store-layout-product-trends-customer-experience-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20home-improvement%20retailer%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20optimize%20store%20layouts%20and%20predict%20product%20trends%2C%20aiming%20to%20enhance%20the%20customer%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nicholas%20Fearn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flowes-ai-retail-store-layout-product-trends-customer-experience-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astronomer%20announce