%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbellroy-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBellroy%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more).%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Lite%20Carry-On%20is%20almost%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20Lite%20Travel%20Pack%2C%20but%20with%20wheels%20and%20a%20handle%20added%20on.%20If%20you've%20spent%20any%20time%20with%20the%20brand%2C%20you%20should%20have%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20you're%20getting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20are%20new%20to%20Bellroy%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20streamlined%20sophistication.%20These%20bags%20don't%20have%20as%20many%20pockets%20and%20compartments%20as%20some%20of%20the%20picks%20on%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-carry-on-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20carry-on%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide%2C%20but%20they%20make%20the%20most%20of%20their%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20writing%20about%20technology%2C%20gadgets%2C%20and%20the%20bags%20to%20carry%20that%20gear%20in.%20My%20wife%20would%20tell%20you%20I%20have%20an%20obsession%20with%20finding%20the%20perfect%20backpack%20and%20weekender%2C%20though%20I%20think%20obsession%20is%20a%20strong%20word.%20Beyond%20putting%20these%20two%20luggage%20pieces%20through%20the%20standard%20tests%2C%20I%20took%20them%20on%20an%20actual%20trip%20to%20see%20how%20they%20fared%20in%20real-world%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229aa70764-1659-42e6-ae47-8212a401b9e1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20specs%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20and%20specs%20of%20Bellroy's%20new%20luggage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20side-by-side%20views%20of%20the%20Bellroy%20Transit%20Carry-On%20suitcase%20in%20black%3A%20one%20showing%20the%20telescoping%20handle%20extended%2C%20and%20the%20other%20showing%20the%20front%20of%20the%20suitcase%20with%20the%20brand%20logo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a80a9f748d8c055f5e2ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Transit%20Carry-On%20is%20the%20brand's%20more%20traditional%20hardshell%20bag.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hard%20shell%20Bellroy%20Transit%20Carry-On%20will%20probably%20be%20the%20more%20popular%20option%20because%20of%20its%20four%20spinning%20wheels%20and%20traditional%20form%20factor.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20Lite%20Carry-On%20because%20of%20its%20potential%20for%20extra%20versatility.%20Its%20exterior%20dimensions%20of%2020.1%20x%2013.6%20x%209.1%20inches%20make%20it%20compact%20enough%20to%20be%20carried%20onto%20any%20airline%20%E2%80%94%20no%20caveats%20required.%20Plus%2C%20its%2038-liter%20capacity%20makes%20it%20very%20workable%20for%20up%20to%20a%20five%20to%20seven-day%20trip%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20person%20or%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20views%20of%20the%20Bellroy%20Lite%20Carry-On%3A%20one%20showing%20the%20upright%20suitcase%20from%20the%20side%20with%20wheels%20and%20handles%2C%20and%20another%20showing%20the%20suitcase%20open%20with%20mesh%20compartments%20exposed%20on%20a%20carpeted%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a81a73d5881a51c1d9acf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Lite%20Carry-On%20is%20a%20soft-sided%2C%20ultra-light%20suitcase%20with%20smart%20internal%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20ideal%20for%20minimalist%20travelers%20or%20short%20weekend%20trips.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lite%20Carry-On%20has%20a%20telescoping%20handle%20that%20locks%20at%2014%2C%2016%2C%20and%2020%20inches%20tall.%20There's%20a%20zipper%20cover%20to%20fully%20enclose%20the%20handle%20when%20it's%20not%20in%20use.%20But%20most%20of%20all%2C%20I%20like%20its%20light%204.6-pound%20weight.%20If%20I'm%20going%20to%20need%20to%20hoist%20a%20bag%20into%20an%20overhead%20bin%2C%20I%20want%20it%20to%20be%20as%20light%20as%20possible.%20Its%20magic%20power%20is%20that%20it%20can%20also%20be%20squashed%20flat%20when%20it's%20not%20in%20use%2C%20either%20at%20home%20or%20at%20the%20hotel.%20It%20has%20the%20combined%20benefits%20of%20a%20duffle%20bag%20and%20a%20wheeled%20carry-on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20hard%20shell%20side%2C%20the%20Transit%20Carry-On%20weighs%206.8%20pounds%2C%20has%20a%2034-liter%20capacity%20(41-liter%20overall%20volume)%2C%20and%20external%20dimensions%20of%2021.9%20x%2013.8%20x%208.9%20inches.%20Its%20telescopic%20handle%20locks%20at%20slightly%20different%20heights%20of%2012%2C%2014%2C%20and%2018%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20these%20bags%20come%20with%20Bellroy's%2010-year%20warranty%20for%20workmanship%20and%20material%20defects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20even%20more%20storage%20space%2C%20there%20is%20an%20identical%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110052659u6f-20%26h%3Df9d7df59ad8d3a407c22515a989cd28c403e89fdaedfdc41e8f11ff227f512a7%26postID%3D686573a9f1b38408f399c377%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftravel%252Fbellroy-rolling-luggage-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbellroy.com%252Fproducts%252Ftransit-carry-on-plus%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETransit%20Carry-On%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20option%20with%20a%2039-liter%20capacity.%20Though%20bigger%2C%20that%20one%20has%20some%20airline%20conditions%20that%20may%20cause%20you%20to%20check%20it%20if%20strict%20enforcement%20occurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d81ccdc-f0dd-4915-aee2-00629bbcddbd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20it's%20like%20to%20use%5C%22%3EFlying%20and%20driving%20with%20Bellroy's%20new%20luggage%20is%20a%20dream%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20first%20inspection%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20filling%20the%20Lite%20Carry-On%20with%20clothes%20for%20a%20weeklong%2C%20seven-day%20trip%20seemed%20daunting.%20It's%20physically%20smaller%20than%20the%20hard%20shell%20version%20and%20doesn't%20look%20cavernous%20inside.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20stuff%20it%20with%20two%20pairs%20of%20jeans%2C%20two%20pairs%20of%20shorts%2C%20two%20pairs%20of%20lounge%20pants%2C%20seven%20T-shirts%2C%20a%20bathing%20suit%2C%20running%20shorts%2C%20a%20fitness%20shirt%2C%20socks%2C%20underwear%2C%20a%20toiletry%20bag%2C%20and%20a%20few%20other%20odds%20and%20ends.%20It%20stretched%20comfortably%20without%20ever%20seeming%20like%20it%20would%20break%20as%20it%20accommodated%20my%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20bellroy%20lite%20carry%20on%20in%20the%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a822985e81483682e494c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20flew%20with%20the%20Bellroy%20Lite%20Carry-On%20and%20found%20it%20surprisingly%20spacious%20considering%20the%20compact%20size.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20main%20compartment%20is%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20bag's%20storage%2C%20but%20the%20opening%20flap's%20two%20zippered%20compartments%20are%20well-portioned%20for%20practical%20use.%20The%20smaller%20top%20one%20is%20ideal%20for%20holding%20socks%20and%20underwear%2C%20but%20it%20could%20also%20be%20used%20for%20other%20toiletries%20or%20travel%20documents.%20I%20used%20the%20larger%20pocket%20below%20it%20for%20my%20workout%20clothes%20on%20the%20way%20out%20to%20my%20vacation%2C%20and%20put%20some%20dirty%20clothes%20I%20wanted%20separated%20in%20it%20on%20the%20way%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20even%20with%20the%20flap%20compartments%20fully%20packed%2C%20it%20didn't%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20packing%20space%20in%20the%20single%20exterior%20pocket.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20fit%20a%20Bluetooth%20speaker%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20a%20rolled-up%20belt%20in%20that%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20putting%20the%20bag%20into%20use%2C%20I%20really%20liked%20its%20flexible%20fabric.%20It%20feels%20thick%20enough%20to%20be%20protective%2C%20but%20I%20was%20unsure%20of%20how%20it%20would%20hold%20up.%20As%20I%20dragged%20the%20bag%20through%20airports%2C%20plopped%20it%20onto%20conveyor%20belts%2C%20and%20lifted%20it%20into%20overhead%20bins%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20watch%20how%20the%20exterior%20fared%20across%20these%20travel%20conditions.%20It%20was%20shoved%20into%20rental%20cars%20and%20fully%20unpacked%20at%20my%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20zippers%20are%20smooth%20and%20never%20got%20caught%20on%20clothes%20or%20pieces%20of%20the%20bag%20itself.%20Even%20when%20my%20bag%20was%20flagged%20by%20TSA%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20open%20it%20and%20reseal%20it%20in%20a%20mild%20panic%2C%20it%20closed%20perfectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20bellroy%20lite%20carry-on%20before%20and%20after%20travel%2C%20with%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20the%20grab%20bar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a82cdf748d8c055f5e30c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20underside%20of%20the%20Lite%20Carry-On%20before%20(left)%20and%20after%20(right)%20travel.%20You%20can%20see%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20the%20grab%20bar%20from%20sliding%20it%20up%20and%20down%20stairs.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20weeklong%20trip%2C%20it%20showed%20the%20most%20signs%20of%20wear%20on%20the%20plastic%20rest%20bar%20underneath%20the%20bag.%20That%20piece%20got%20visibly%20scratched%20up%2C%20but%20the%20backside%20of%20the%20fabric%20only%20showed%20faint%20signs%20of%20being%20touched%2C%20even%20though%20it%20took%20the%20brunt%20of%20sliding%20against%20stairs%20and%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20used%20the%20hard%20shell%20Transit%20Carry-On%20for%20our%20trip.%20She%20was%20skeptical%20about%20its%20non-expandable%2034-liter%20capacity%2C%20but%20managed%20to%20make%20it%20work%20for%20a%20seven-day%20trip.%20As%20someone%20new%20to%20packing%20cubes%2C%20she%20was%20unsure%20about%20keeping%20both%20of%20the%20cubes%20attached%20initially.%20But%20she%20did%20fill%20them%20and%20even%20managed%20to%20squeeze%20a%20few%20items%20underneath%20them%20to%20use%20even%20more%20space.%20After%20the%20first%20leg%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20she%20commented%20that%20the%20luggage%20worked%20better%20than%20she%20expected.%20It%20fit%20enough%20and%20was%20functionally%20elegant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225299%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20bellroy%20transite%20carry-on%20unzipped%20and%20open%20on%20a%20wood%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a83593d5881a51c1d9b21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223974%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Transit%20Carry-On%20has%20built-in%20packing%20cubes%20that%20you%20can%20use%20to%20keep%20your%20items%20organized%20during%20travel.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EManeuvering%20the%20hard%20shell%20bag%20through%20the%20airport%2C%20into%20an%20overhead%20bin%2C%20and%20into%20the%20trunk%20of%20a%20rental%20car%20worked%20great.%20It%20never%20felt%20flimsy%20or%20showed%20signs%20of%20bending%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5bfb7cd-52c5-44f2-9eac-f06212cfa7b1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Durability%5C%22%3ERepairability%20is%20the%20standout%20feature%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20first%20impressions%20through%20actual%20use%20on%20a%20weeklong%20trip%2C%20the%20materials%20of%20both%20pieces%20of%20luggage%20stood%20out.%20Nothing%20about%20either%20bag%20felt%20cheap%2C%20de