20sweaty%20New%20Yorkers%20like%20me%2C%20that%20means%20one%20thing%3A%20it's%20officially%20mini%20fan%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20stand%20being%20hot%2C%20and%20summer%20presents%20far%20too%20many%20opportunities%20for%20that%20than%20I%20care%20for.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20bought%20myself%20a%20rechargeable%20handheld%20mini%20fan%20that%20folds%20into%20a%20desktop%20fan%2C%20and%20it%20has%20drastically%20improved%20the%20way%20I%20feel%20about%20leaving%20the%20house%20in%20the%20summer.%20I%20love%20this%20little%20fan%20from%20Jisulife%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20my%20responsibility%20to%20%3Cem%3Ehighly%20%3C%2Fem%3Erecommend%20you%20buy%20it.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20take%20it%20everywhere.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20fan%20comes%20with%20me%20every%20time%20I%20leave%20the%20house%20in%20the%20summer%20and%20especially%20on%20trips.%20You%20can%20catch%20me%20fanning%20myself%20on%20the%20subway%20platform%2C%20at%20the%20park%2C%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20while%20sitting%20outside%20at%20a%20restaurant%2C%20and%20pretty%20much%20any%20other%20place%20that%20isn't%20air-conditioned%20to%20a%20crisp%2060%20degrees.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20asks%20me%20about%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20so%20great%20for%20kids.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20my%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20an%20avowed%20mini%20fan%20hater%20%E2%80%94%20has%20conceded%20that%20it's%20pretty%20nifty%2C%20and%20once%20even%20said%20he%20wanted%20one%20(though%20he%20will%20deny%20this).%20I%20recently%20hosted%20my%20cousins%20and%20their%20three%20little%20girls%20in%20NYC%20during%20100%2B%20degree%20days%2C%20and%20the%20kids%20were%20always%20fighting%20over%20control%20of%20the%20fan.%20It%20saved%20us%20from%20a%20few%20(literal)%20meltdowns%20with%20cranky%20kids%20walking%20in%20the%20heat.%20The%20fan%20blades%20are%20thin%20plastic%20and%20stop%20spinning%20when%20touched%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20worry%20about%20hurting%20little%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20love%20that%20it%20folds%20up.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I've%20looked%20at%20other%20mini%20fans%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20love%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20classic%20cage%20fan%20%E2%80%94%20and%20don't%20even%20get%20me%20started%20on%20those%20wearable%20neck%20fans.%20Plus%2C%20I%20have%20so%20much%20crap%20in%20my%20bag%20that%20exposed%20fan%20blades%20are%20bound%20to%20get%20tangled%20in%20my%20headphones%20or%20keychain.%20The%20Jisulife%20fan%20stores%20compactly%20when%20not%20in%20use%2C%20and%20I%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20it%20accidentally%20turning%20on%20in%20my%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can%20also%20use%20it%20as%20a%20desk%20fan.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20handle%20folds%20back%20so%20that%20the%20fan%20can%20sit%20flat%20on%20a%20surface%20and%20provide%20you%20with%20blissfully%20cool%20air.%20I've%20used%20it%20at%20work%2C%20and%20I%20always%20take%20it%20with%20me%20when%20I%20travel%20to%20use%20as%20a%20bedside%20fan%20in%20a%20pinch.%20That%20way%2C%20I%20never%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20whether%20the%20sleeping%20accommodations%20will%20be%20as%20frosty%20as%20I%20prefer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20doubles%20as%20a%20flashlight%20and%20a%20phone%20charger.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I'd%20be%20content%20if%20it%20only%20functioned%20as%20a%20fan%2C%20but%20it's%20pretty%20great%20that%20I%20can%20also%20use%20it%20as%20a%20portable%20battery%20in%20a%20pinch.%20I%20have%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20use%20for%20the%20flashlight%20feature%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20purchased%20this%20fan%20three%20times%20now.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20because%20it's%20broken%20or%20anything%2C%20but%20rather%20because%20I've%20left%20it%20in%20numerous%20destinations%20over%20the%20years.%20Still%2C%20I%20think%20it%20says%20something%20that%20I've%20always%20come%20back%20to%20the%20same%20fan%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20rebuy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fww