0the%20system%20more%20viable.%20So%20you%20see%2C%20with%20a%20subsidy%2C%20the%20project%20would%20run%20for%20around%20four%20years.%20But%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20it%20run%20forever.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20energy%20becomes%20an%20enabler%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHow%20can%20energy%20access%20transform%20the%20villages%20of%20India%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Sameer%20and%20Anshuman%20bent%20their%20heads%20over%20the%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20contextualise%20their%20concerns%2C%20we%20revisit%20a%202015%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20which%20underscored%20that%20even%20though%20India%20was%20officially%20declared%20100%20percent%20electrified%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20just%2010%20percent%20of%20homes%20in%20a%20village%20had%20to%20have%20electricity%20to%20meet%20the%20criteria%20%E2%80%94%2017%20percent%20of%20homes%20were%20still%20without%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20bothered%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20ideating%20on%20the%20best%20way%20to%20create%20impact%20in%20the%20villages%2C%20we%20struck%20upon%20the%20idea%20of%20energy%20access.%20We%E2%80%99re%20talking%20about%20a%20time%20when%20fossil%20fuel%20prices%20were%20steadily%20rising.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20you%20had%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418409%2Findia-solar-power-electricity-bill-savings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20renewable%20energy%20becoming%20more%20accessible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20take%20both%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20the%20falling%20prices%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20the%20rising%20prices%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20%E2%80%94%20and%20create%20a%20social%20impact%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sameer%20mentions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%2