201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-2-1752772503.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Communities%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20the%20solar%20microgrids%20have%20been%20installed%20now%20have%20an%20additional%20source%20of%20income%20through%20the%20use%20of%20solar%20power%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-2-1752772503.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-2-1752772503-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-2-1752772503-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-2-1752772503-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-2-1752772503-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471790%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECommunities%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20the%20solar%20microgrids%20have%20been%20installed%20now%20have%20an%20additional%20source%20of%20income%20through%20the%20use%20of%20solar%20power%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20that%20snake%20bites%20are%20a%20prevalent%20problem%20in%20the%20Indian%20villages%2C%20Sameer%20says%20the%20solution%20is%20to%20light%20up%20these%20pockets.%20%E2%80%9CStreet%20lights%20can%20make%20the%20villages%20safer.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20that%20snake%20bites%20become%20rarer%20occurrences%20when%20the%20roads%20are%20lit%20up.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20where%20the%20villagers%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20pawn%20their%20freedom%20for%20the%20fear%20of%20getting%20bitten.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sometimes%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20entry%20of%20snakes%20into%20a%20certain%20area%20that%20gets%20curbed%20because%20of%20the%20now%20lit-up%20roads%2C%20other%20times%20it%E2%80%99s%20simply%20the%20locals%20feeling%20safer%20because%20they%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20path.%20Suchita%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20our%20village%20got%20light%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20scared%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20roads%20late%20at%20night.%20Even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20snake%20in%20our%20path%2C%20we%20see%20it%20and%20move%20away.%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20not%20just%20snakes%20but%20even%20elephants%20%E2%80%94%20Jharkhand%20is%20home%20to%2014%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelephant%20corridors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20have%20started%20being%20wary%20of%20the%20lit-up%20village.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20stray%20in%20anymore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELight%20became%20the%20antidote%20to%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20energy-resilient%20communities%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rains%20would%20bow%20out%20for%20the%20year%2C%20Maharashtra-based%20farmer%20Ambadas%20Bhoye%20would%20proceed%20to%20pack%20his%20bags.%20The%20end%20of%20the%20monsoon%20season%20meant%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20his%20village%20of%20Tulyachapada.%20The%20paucity%20of%20water%20made%20it%20impossible%20to%20irrigate%20the%20land%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%20And%20so%2C%20Ambadas%20would%20migrate%20to%20the%20main%20city%20looking%20for%20work%20that%20would%20help%20him%20eke%20out%20a%20living%20until%20the%20rains%20returned%20once%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20well.%20Ambadas%20earned%20Rs%20215%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20good%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20in%202019%2C%20something%20changed.%20That%20year%2C%20when%20the%20rains%20ebbed%2C%20Ambadas%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sad.%20He%20simply%20went%20to%20his%20field%20and%20turned%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424712%2Fanand-jain-iit-roorkee-alumnus-creates-india-largest-agrivoltaic-solar-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar-powered%20irrigation%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20fields%20of%20groundnut%2C%20%3Cem%3Eokra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lady%20finger)%2C%20pumpkins%2C%20and%20beans%20are%20thriving.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-1752773941.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ambadas'%20fields%20are%20thriving%20with%20groundnut%2C%20pumpkins%20and%20beans%20because%20of%20the%20solar%20powered%20irrigation%20system%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-1752773941.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-1752773941-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-1752773941-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-1752773941-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fenergy-access-1752773941-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471803%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmbadas%E2%80%99%20fields%20are%20thriving%20with%20groundnut%2C%20pumpkins%20and%20beans%20because%20of%20the%20solar%20powered%20irrigation%20system%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C