0in%20villages%20without%20steady%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20parts%20of%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20hilly%20terrain%2C%20poor%20infrastructure%20leaves%20farmers%20with%20few%20options.%20Crops%20are%20grown%20with%20care%2C%20only%20to%20decay%20before%20they%20can%20be%20sold.%20But%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Porba%2C%20a%20gentle%20shift%20is%20underway.%20One%20young%20man%20is%20helping%20change%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2026%2C%20Swuyievezo%20Dzudo%20has%20built%20a%20low-cost%20solar%20dryer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20simple%2C%20electricity-free%20device%20that%E2%80%99s%20helping%20farmers%20preserve%20their%20produce%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328356%2Fhyderabad-recykal-marketplace-sell-waste-online-empower-scrap-dealers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20waste%2C%20and%20earn%20better%20incomes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20idea%20is%20offering%20a%20path%20forward%20that%20relies%20not%20on%20power%20grids%20or%20big%20machinery%2C%20but%20on%20sunlight%2C%20local%20materials%2C%20and%20listening%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20his%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20botany%20to%20the%20barnyard%3A%20A%20scholar%20returns%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Swuyievezo%20Dzudo%20came%20back%20to%20his%20village%20of%20Porba%20after%20finishing%20his%20postgraduation%20studies%20from%20St%20Joseph%20University%2C%20Dimapur%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20help%20farmers%20like%20the%20ones%20he%20grew%20up%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752