%20to%20preserve%20the%20excess%20produce%20of%20all%20kinds%20of%20crops%20without%20affecting%20the%20quality%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20Swuyievezo%E2%80%99s%20low-cost%20solar%20dryer%20bridges%20the%20gap.%20Built%20using%20locally%20available%20and%20recycled%20materials%2C%20the%20dryer%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20affordable%2C%20durable%2C%20and%20effective%20%E2%80%94%20a%20true%20game%20changer%20for%20rural%20farming%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20bamboo%20and%20wood%20for%20the%20main%20structure%20because%20these%20are%20abundant%20in%20our%20village%20and%20inexpensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Bamboo%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20lightweight%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20sustainable%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20rural%20construction.%20To%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F448564%2Fcommunities-come-together-to-tackle-heat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabsorb%20heat%20efficiently%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20dryer%20incorporates%20an%20ingenious%20solar%20accumulator%20made%20from%20empty%20aluminium%20beer%20cans.%20These%20cans%20store%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20heat%2C%20creating%20a%20consistent%20warming%20effect%20inside%20the%20drying%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20retain%20heat%20and%20protect%20the%20produce%20from%20harsh%20direct%20sunlight%2C%20Swuyievezo%20initially%20used%20acrylic%20sheets%2C%20but%20later%20switched%20to%20glass%20sheets%2C%20which%20are%20more%20durable%20and%20better%20for%20insulation.%20The%20drying%20chamber%20is%20lined%20with%20UV-protective%20sheets%20that%20filter%20out%20harmful%20rays%2C%20shielding%20the%20produce%20from%20damage%20and%20keeping%20insects%20and%20pests%20at%20bay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20exhaust%20fan%2C%20powered%20by%20a%20small%20solar%20panel%2C%20ensures%20continuous%20airflow%20and%20removes%20excess%20moisture%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20an%20optimal%20drying%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20was%20balancing%20heat%20retention%20with%20proper%20airflow%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20innovator%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CToo%20much%20humidity%20would%20cause%20mould%2C%20but%20too%20little%20airflow%20would%20slow%20the%20drying%20process.%20We%20experimented%20with%20fan%20placement%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20layouts%20until%20we%20found%20the%20right%20balance.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20structure%20of%20the%20solar%20dryer%20is%20made%20using%20bamboo%20and%20wood%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20low%20for%20all%20farmers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471046%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20structure%20of%20the%20solar%20dryer%20is%20made%20using%20bamboo%20and%20wood%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20low%20for%20all%20farmers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fan%20itself%20is%20repurposed%20from%20discarded%20computer%20or%20laptop%20parts%20%E2%80%94%20another%20small%20but%20significant%20touch%20that%20keeps%20costs%20low%20and%20makes%20the%20system%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20solution%20that%20fits%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECost%20is%20a%20critical%20factor%20for%20rural%20farmers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20survive%20on%20modest%20incomes.%20Industrial%20dryers%20often%20cost%20lakhs%20%E2%80%94%20far%20beyond%20what%20smallholder%20farmers%20can%20afford.%20Swuyievezo%E2%80%99s%20solar%20dryer%20offers%20a%20much-needed%20alternative%3A%20affordable%2C%20customisable%2C%20and%20built%20from%20materials%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20strain%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20pocket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-foot%20model%20costs%20approximately%20Rs%207%2C000%2C%20while%20larger%20units%20measuring%2010%20by%2010%20feet%20range%20between%20Rs%2025%2C000%20and%20Rs%2030%2C000.%20The%20lower%20cost%20is%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20use%20of%20readily%20available%20materials%20such%20as%20bamboo%2C%20wood%2C%20aluminium%20cans%2C%20UV%20sheets%2C%20and%20solar%20panels%20%E2%80%94%20all%20chosen%20to%20reduce%20expenses%20without%20compromising%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291233%2Fkerala-man-uses-steel-builds-eco-friendly-low-cost-home-thats-earthquake-fire-resistant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20is%20low%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20far%20we%20have%20been%20providing%20the%20solar%20dryers%20free%20of%20charge%20to%20farmers%20in%20five%20villages%20of%20Nagaland%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20every%20farmer%2C%20regardless%20of%20income%2C%20can%20access%20this%20technology%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%20The%20five%20beneficiary%20villages%20%E2%80%94%20Porba%2C%20Thuvopisu%2C%20Dzulhami%2C%20Runguzu%2C%20and%20Ciepoketa%20%E2%80%94%20have%20seen%20about%20500%20farmers%20receive%20these%20dryers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20on%20local%20farmers%20has%20been%20powerful%20and%20immediate.%20Verazo%2C%20who%20constructed%20two%20solar%20dryers%20on%20his%20farm%20with%20Swuyievezo%E2%80%99s%20guidance%2C%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20quality%20of%20dried%20kiwi%20and%20other%20fruits%20is%20excellent.%20The%20dryer%20preserves%20the%20flavour%20and%20colour%2C%20and%20the%20shelf%20life%20is%20extended.%20We%20can%20now%20sell%20dried%20fruits%20months%20after%20harvest%2C%20which%20opens%20up%20new%20market%20opportunities%20and%20better%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172337.992_11zon-1752666832.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22To%20absorb%20heat%20efficiently%2C%20the%20dryer%20incorporates%20an%20ingenious%20solar%20accumulator%20made%20from%20empty%20aluminium%20beer%20cans%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172337.992_11zon-1752666832.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172337.992_11zon-1752666832-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20h