precise%20environmental%20control.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202024%2C%20Anil%20procured%20one%20tonne%20of%20saffron%20bulbs%20for%20Rs%20eight%20lakh%20from%20Pampore.%20%E2%80%9COf%20this%2C%20we%20could%20use%20700%20kg%20that%20met%20the%20criteria%20for%20cultivation.%20It%20is%20advised%20to%20grow%20saffron%20bulbs%20weighing%20seven%20grams%3B%20otherwise%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20result%20in%20flowering.%20We%20nurtured%20the%20remaining%20bulbs%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20detail%20of%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20indoor%20farm%20is%20tailored%20to%20replicate%20the%20conditions%20of%20a%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20field.%20From%20regulating%20temperatures%20between%20eight%20to%2025%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%20maintaining%20humidity%20levels%2C%20every%20parameter%20was%20fine-tuned%20to%20perfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20saffron%20bloomed%2C%20Anil%20says%2C%20stringent%20hygiene%20practices%20were%20implemented%2C%20akin%20to%20intensive%20care%20cleanliness%20standards.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wash%20our%20hands%20with%2070%20percent%20Isopropyl%20Alcohol%20(IPA)%20solution%20(a%20disinfectant)%20and%20we%20wear%20hand%20gloves%20and%20protective%20gear%20before%20entering%20the%20indoor%20farm.%20This%20prevents%20any%20possible%20contamination%20or%20fungal%20growth%20in%20saffron%20bulbs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20meticulously%20regulates%20carbon%20dioxide%20levels%2C%20light%20exposure%2C%20and%20bulb%20hygiene%20to%20ensure%20a%20thriving%20crop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20November%2C%20his%20efforts%20bore%20fruit%2C%20as%20he%20proudly%20harvested%201%2C600%20grams%20of%20saffron.%20Following%20the%20harvest%2C%20he%20dried%20the%20delicate%20red%20stigmas%20and%20ensured%20their%20safe%20storage%20to%20prevent%20fungal%20growth.%20Selling%20it%20at%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram%2C%20Anil%20reaped%20a%20substantial%20Rs%20eight%20lakh