ir%20timely%20harvest.%20Sharing%20her%20experience%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20visited%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20saffron%20fields%20captivated%20us.%20We%20wanted%20to%20bring%20a%20piece%20of%20that%20charm%20back%20home.%20The%20excitement%20of%20harvesting%20our%20own%20saffron%20made%20it%20worthwhile.%20The%20quality%20difference%20is%20striking%3B%20we%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20realise%20much%20of%20what%20we%20previously%20used%20was%20not%20authentic.%20Lab%20tests%20confirmed%20our%20saffron%E2%80%99s%20purity%20%E2%80%94%20just%20two%20strands%20turn%20dishes%20a%20rich%20golden%20hue%2C%20unlike%20the%20quick%2C%20artificial-looking%20colour%20of%20market-bought%20saffron.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20our%20homemade%20sweets%20are%20enhanced%20with%20our%20own%20authentic%20saffron.%20It%E2%80%99s%20wonderful%20to%20have%20brought%20a%20slice%20of%20Kashmiri%20essence%20to%20our%20little%20home%20in%20Indore%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%2C%20too%2C%20is%20immensely%20satisfied%20with%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20long-term%20business%20of%20long-term%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes%2C%20emphasising%20the%20patience%20required%20in%20the%20initial%20years.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20merging%20traditional%20farming%20wisdom%20with%20modern%20technology%2C%20we%20have%20crafted%20a%20sustainable%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F457942%2Fgrow-saffron-indoors-noida-ramesh-gera-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elucrative%20venture%20within%20our%20own%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20would%20go%2025%20km%20away%20to%20tend%20to%20my%20floriculture%20farm.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20brought%20the%20farm%20to%20my%20home%20itself.%20This%20venture%20is%20part%20of%20my%20retirement%20plan.%20It%20offers%20me%20financial%20security%20while%20keeping%20me%20engaged%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5